data.description: Deal fell through! Embrace SOARING CEILINGS and HUGE BACK YARD and PATIO in  amazing FRANKLIN, TN! NO HOA!! LOVELY KID/PET/ARTIST friendly home, fenced & gated. Very close to SCHOOLS, DOWNTOWN FRANKLIN, THE FACTORY, & COOL SPRINGS! Lovely open floor plan. Living & dining room have SOARING CEILINGS w/HARDWOOD FLRS & cozy FIREPLACE. Kitchen is tiled w/NEW SINGLE BASIN SINK & 2 pantries. Master bedrm w/HARDWOOD FLRS, WALK IN CLOSET & standard closet. Master bathrm w/NEW MARBLE VANITY w/full bath. 2nd downstairs large bdrm exits out to HUGE PATIO which can be CONVERTED TO A RENTAL UNIT. 2 Upstairs bdrms w/HARDWOOD FLOORS have Jack & Jill bathroom w/NEW MARBLE VANITY w/full bath. Bedrms are located in the back of the house, away from street. HUGE DRIVEWAY! STORAGE SHED! Forget renting!
